Dobro jutro, detektive.

49
00:01:55,082 --> 00:01:56,082
Jutro.

50
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:57,015
Maks.

51
00:01:57,118 --> 00:01:59,418
Uvijek djeveruša, nikad detektiv.

52
