176
00:05:55,255 --> 00:05:57,022
I opet natrag unatrag.

177
00:05:58,192 --> 00:06:00,092
Je li vaš sigurnosni sustav ožičen ili Wi-Fi?

178
00:06:00,194 --> 00:06:01,194
